summary:
This spell allows spellcasters to alter a creature's sight, granting them the ability to see in the dark.

:For the passive feature inherent to races and monsters, see {{SAI|Darkvision (Passive Feature).}}
:For the Way of the Shadow Monk ability, see {{SAI|Shadow Arts: Darkvision.}}

description:
Channel the stones' magic to control the Crown of Karsus and dominate the Netherbrain.

The caster must Channelling Karsus' Compulsion|channel this spell until their next turn for it to take effect.

Ends if caster is {{Cond|Incapacitated, Stunned, Polymorphed, or Knocked Out.}}
